title: Flash Back Lil Duval Interview and More
itunes:title: Flash Back Lil Duval Interview and More
description:
Today on the show we flashed back to when the writer Humble the Poet stopped by and spoke about his book "Unlearned" and his start to success. Also, we flashed back to when Lil Duval stopped by and promoted another hit "Pull Up" and more. Moreover, we flashed back to the funniest callers for "Slander the Breakfast Club" just to keep them humbled.
